definitions.definition: Strips of material used as festive decoration , especially in the colours of the national flag.
( nautical ) A thin cloth of woven wool from which flags are made; it is light enough to spread in a gentle wind but resistant to fraying in a strong wind.

main_definition: Strips of material used as festive decoration , especially in the colours of the national flag.
secondary_definitions: ( nautical ) A thin cloth of woven wool from which flags are made; it is light enough to spread in a gentle wind but resistant to fraying in a strong wind.

definitions.definition: Any of various songbirds of the genus Emberiza , having short bills and brown or gray plumage .

main_definition: Any of various songbirds of the genus Emberiza , having short bills and brown or gray plumage .

definitions.definition: A warm, often hooded infant garment, as outerwear or sleepwear, similar to a sleeper or sleepsack ; especially as baby bunting or bunting bag .

main_definition: A warm, often hooded infant garment, as outerwear or sleepwear, similar to a sleeper or sleepsack ; especially as baby bunting or bunting bag .

definitions.definition: A strong timber ; a stout prop .
An old boys' game, played with sticks and a small piece of wood.

secondary_definitions: A strong timber ; a stout prop .
( obsolete ) An old boys' game, played with sticks and a small piece of wood.
